  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single-blinded RCT evaluating the value of up-positioning of the testes as
      supportive therapy in patients receiving antimicrobial treatment due to acute bacterial
      orchitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
