  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  acute orchitis confirmed clinically and in scrotal ultrasound

          -  age &gt;=18 yrs

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  previous treatment of orchitis,

          -  need for exploration of the scrotum,

          -  need for hospitalization,

          -  physical and mental status not allowing for up-positioning of the testes during
             treatment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
